 &HT;    It's your domain
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ It is playtime! Kid's Domain at
www.kidsdomain.com/games/index.html offers online games for even
the slowest computer. The games are organized by plug-ins, and the
site tells you which games are compatible with most computers.
Games include ones from ``Sesame Street,'' the ``Teletubbies'' and
Disney. Click your way through a whole lot of fun!
</P>
<P>
   ONLY 11 DAYS LEFT
</P>
<P>
   Get in the Christmas spirit at www.night.net/christmas
</P>
<P>
   /index.html-ssi with a wide range of links on the ``Christmas!
Christmas! Christmas!'' site from Not Just for Kids. You can check
out Christmas traditions, the songs of the season, stories and
poems. There's even a spot to click on a Christmas countdown
tracking the hours, minutes and seconds until St. Nick embarks on
his worldwide trip.
