the free software movement. By Hiawatha Bray. 780 words. PHOTO
</P>
<P>
   FINANCE-HOOKER (Undated) _ Investor who began investing late
needs to concentrate intensely on building his accounts, which will
probably support his financial stability during retirement. By
Kenneth Hooker.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
