<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-13 16:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7625 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a BC-SCI-BRODY-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      12-13 1147
