</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ We examine recent reports that candles are a health
hazard. Among the concerns expressed in news reports: that metal
wicks can release lead into the home; the flames can send out
dangerous amounts of soot; and that melting wax can release toxins.
By JESSIE MILLIGAN. Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category.
Accompanied by BC-CANDLE-TIPS. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
