<P>
   WEB-ALLFEMALE &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ All-female, all-the-time women's supersites are
battling for attention _ and dollars _ on the Web. The three top
contenders, including Oprah's newest addition, Oxygen.com, boast
powerful partnerships, media execs on the masthead and multimedia
plans. Who will win? Grab your mouse, and help make the decision.
By CATHERINE NEWTON. Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
nn
</P>
