<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   An article that moved Saturday on a speech by Vice President Al
Gore incorrectly called Atlanta Life Insurance Co. the nation's
largest African American-owned and -controlled company. It is the
nation's largest African American-controlled stockholder-owned life
insurance firm.
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
