<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-13 21:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7912 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u p BC-CAMPAIGN-MCCAIN-BOS &LR;      12-13 1195
